{"tid":929350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友係人地面前係好樂觀既形象 查實係我面前負多於正","createTime":"2018-12-05T13:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T02:04:50.000Z","uid":25915,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fac878aff3b57fed089b40ae6853fc1b684a49fe","tid":929350,"uid":25915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:24:42.000Z","msg":"唔知有無巴打女朋友都係咁<br />\n首先，我唔反對人信教 <br />\n亦都覺得有信仰既人較為樂觀 <br />\n但以我女朋友為例 佢由細返教會到大 <br />\n係教會入面 人人都好似好樂觀好積極既態度 甚至乎只要你一唔開心 個個都會關心你 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但對於佢黎講就唔係一件好事 <br />\n佢本身個人都唔夠自信 佢覺得自己已經失敗左既時候仲要重覆話俾人知 個挫折感好似更重 <br />\n所以佢就習慣左收收埋埋 直到拍左拖之後 <br />\n呢幾年黎我都做左佢既樹窿 但久而久之佢呻完都會發下晦氣 唉 其實我都有壓力 我都想搵人宣泄 但我好怕同佢呻反而令佢個人對事物既睇法更負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e657c6a611a8d1de4da408b6e9b5957a5ac0b0","tid":929350,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"搵多個女朋友"},{"pid":"7d630c514b3e51e5d9f5b7f45d23c872d131cf58","tid":929350,"uid":86151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"但佢只可以同你講<br />\n你係佢惟一"},{"pid":"e2ab7a82a1f122f592d280c700f52f60bc967ed1","tid":929350,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"咁你跟你女友一齊去信教，你呻嘅時候就好多人關心你，就唔使影響女友，咁你女友又可以繼續同你呻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4d3a027da96582802198337578bd4c458d0557","tid":929350,"uid":25915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d630c514b3e51e5d9f5b7f45d23c872d131cf58","tid":929350,"uid":86151,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"但佢只可以同你講<br />\n你係佢惟一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:34:30.000Z","msg":"我自己都係咁諗 所以我想令到佢個人變得更有熱誠咁過生活 佢有時會話 生存係到都唔知有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc665bd798d1070f8150b1381ac022829df8c966","tid":929350,"uid":25915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2ab7a82a1f122f592d280c700f52f60bc967ed1","tid":929350,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"咁你跟你女友一齊去信教，你呻嘅時候就好多人關心你，就唔使影響女友，咁你女友又可以繼續同你呻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"我求知慾都高 我怕係佢教會聽經會駁嘴 雖然佢教會既人都識我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca58b28ce343505c0c65440b968b6ac9d89bef9","tid":929350,"uid":208132,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"我女朋友有時候都係咁<br />\n但無辦法，愛佢就要愛佢嘅全部，正面，負面都要，咁先叫愛"},{"pid":"438ff632bcfb8e697ed34b60d2b00e140061582c","tid":929350,"uid":25915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aca58b28ce343505c0c65440b968b6ac9d89bef9","tid":929350,"uid":208132,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"我女朋友有時候都係咁<br />\n但無辦法，愛佢就要愛佢嘅全部，正面，負面都要，咁先叫愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"講得無錯阿巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cf787d5fa549e75d431e5e0ebde9b2a65724b3","tid":929350,"uid":208132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438ff632bcfb8e697ed34b60d2b00e140061582c","tid":929350,"uid":25915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aca58b28ce343505c0c65440b968b6ac9d89bef9","tid":929350,"uid":208132,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"我女朋友有時候都係咁<br />\n但無辦法，愛佢就要愛佢嘅全部，正面，負面都要，咁先叫愛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"講得無錯阿巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"你認同我嘅證明巴打你都真